{"tid":2098643,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"的士佬真係自私，有密切接觸都唔想去驗咁","createTime":"2020-07-07T15:31:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T01:25:30.000Z","uid":251118,"like":61,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"aa72f2cef4ddedd492267e73fa169826b238e3cf","tid":2098643,"uid":251118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T15:31:50.000Z","msg":"岩岩小弟坐的士途中，聽到個的士司機問另一個行家<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;你去唔去驗？政府呼籲去過新發茶餐廳食過飯都去驗wor&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n我聽到就問下個的士司機係咪去過新發食飯，佢都唔應我<br />\n<br />\n到我落車，善意咁講句&rdquo;司機大哥，如果你真係去過個到食飯，就真係驗下&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n個司機大哥就屌9我&rdquo;屌，要中就中嫁啦，洗乜鬼驗&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nd隱影傳播咪就係咁黎囉！<br />\n<br />\n聽個的士佬口吻，新發有機會係d的士佬聚腳點。<br />\n<br />\n仲要今日其中一個確診者係的士佬，大家最近就少坐的士為妙<br />\n<br />\n如果有人識KH4148(如果我無睇錯) 既司機大哥，唔該提佢真係走去驗一驗"},{"pid":"b0d8a3228f9585fde36fbb48917cae228bb374ce","tid":2098643,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T15:33:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fda23d66444e2f27eeee17dbb6a9e4b0bc1e50f4","tid":2098643,"uid":4309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T15:38:49.000Z","msg":"屌咩dc9咪累死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3fd7d45efee113fef48cbda8b4848afbda14418","tid":2098643,"uid":15605,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T15:49:04.000Z","msg":"樓主去驗下好喎"},{"pid":"e5eecdf1132dbfa494efb6e16c73d0aca750a6cd","tid":2098643,"uid":24457,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T15:49:56.000Z","msg":"你都要驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"095716acc743619aa05d89a316b5ab3add817ff4","tid":2098643,"uid":76591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T15:50:06.000Z","msg":"咩野有機會，佢地日日響度打躉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6da59a07db0b8864efda4ab04